+# Mission Control OS — Free Deployment Guide
+
+## Stack (All Free)
+- **Railway** — Next.js app + PostgreSQL (free tier, $5 credit)
+- **Supabase** — Auth (free tier, unlimited)
+- **Groq** — AI (free tier, llama-3.1-8b-instant, no CC)
+
+---
+
+## Step 1: Supabase Auth (5 min)
+1. Create project at https://supabase.com
+2. Go to Settings → API
+3. Copy `Project URL` → `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`
+4. Copy `anon public` key → `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
+5. Settings → Authentication → Enable Email, Google (optional), GitHub (optional)
+
+## Step 2: Groq AI (2 min, FREE)
+1. Sign up at https://console.groq.com (no credit card)
+2. API Keys → Create key
+3. Copy key → `GROQ_API_KEY`
+
+## Step 3: Railway Deploy (10 min)
+1. Push this repo to GitHub
+2. Go to https://railway.app → New Project → Deploy from GitHub
+3. Add PostgreSQL plugin
+4. Set env vars:
+   ```
+   DATABASE_URL        = (auto-provided by Railway PostgreSQL plugin)
+   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL    = your supabase url
+   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = your supabase anon key
+   NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL = https://your-app.up.railway.app
+   GROQ_API_KEY        = gsk_...
+   ```
+5. Railway auto-runs `prisma migrate deploy` + `prisma db seed` via `package.json` build script
+
+## Step 4: Test Demo Mode
+- Visit your Railway URL
+- Click **Try Demo — No Sign Up Required**
+- Should land on dashboard with pre-seeded data
+- Test: Create mission, complete it, check achievements, try Focus timer, open AI Coach
+
+---
+
+## Features Working in Free Tier
+- ✅ Demo mode (no auth needed)
+- ✅ Full mission CRUD
+- ✅ Campaigns
+- ✅ Focus timer + ambient audio (Web Audio API, no files)
+- ✅ Achievements + XP system
+- ✅ AI features (Groq — briefing, coach, goal breakdown, weekly plan)
+- ✅ GlowBackground canvas
+- ✅ ASMR ambients: Bubble Pop 🫧, Lo-Fi Vinyl 🎵, Rain 🌧️, Forest 🌲, etc.
+
+## What Requires Upgrade
+- Email sending (Resend) — for magic link auth
+- Sentry error tracking — optional
+- PostHog analytics — optional
